    "body": "Regarding the reason for choosing the block with lower number, maybe you can try to read the paper we linked here. \r\n\r\nAnd about the variable names, I think `number, headNumber` is better. `current` here refers to the local head header, and the `header` refers to a header given by a remote peer(so no guarantee it can be the canonical chain head).",
